---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for CLI Tools Guide — how we handle data, cookies, and ads.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="mb-6 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400">
      <ol class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400">Home</a></li>
        <li><span class="mx-1">›</span></li>
        <li class="text-gray-800 dark:text-slate-200 font-medium" aria-current="page">Privacy Policy</li>
      </ol>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="prose-tool">
      <p>CLI Tools Guide respects your privacy. This page explains what data we collect and how we use it.</p>

      <h2>Data We Collect</h2>
      <p>We do not require user accounts. The site may collect anonymous analytics data (page views, browser, device) via third-party services to improve the site experience.</p>

      <h2>Advertising</h2>
      <p>We display ads provided by third-party ad networks such as Google AdSense. These providers may use cookies or similar technologies to serve personalized ads. We do not share personally identifiable information with advertisers.</p>

      <h2>Cookies &amp; Tracking</h2>
      <p>Third-party services may set cookies. If you prefer not to be tracked, use your browser privacy settings or opt out via the ad provider controls.</p>

      <h2>Third Parties</h2>
      <p>We may link to external resources (GitHub, official docs). We are not responsible for external sites' privacy practices.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about privacy? Email <a href="mailto:lucky071118@gmail.com">lucky071118@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

